🌙 Step 1: Apply Modern Dark Theme (FlatLaf)

Default Swing L&F is outdated. Replace it with:

👉 FlatLaf


---

📥 Add FlatLaf (Offline Friendly)

Since you’re on a corporate network:

Option A:

Download JAR from: 👉 https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/com/formdev/flatlaf/

Get:

flatlaf-3.x.jar

Put it in:

C:\dev-tools\libs\

Add it in IntelliJ (same way you added H2 jar)


---

🧠 Apply Dark Theme

📄 Update MainFrame.java (VERY IMPORTANT)

import com.formdev.flatlaf.FlatDarkLaf;

public static void main(String[] args) {

    try {
        FlatDarkLaf.setup(); // 🔥 DARK THEME
    } catch (Exception e) {
        e.printStackTrace();
    }

    SwingUtilities.invokeLater(() -> {
        new MainFrame().setVisible(true);
    });
}


